Package: seahorse
Title: Tools for Analyzing Seahorse Bioenergetic Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "William", 
        family = "Oldham", 
        email = "wm.oldham@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3029-4866")
    )
Description: This package provides tools to import Seahorse data from an exported
    Excel file; calculate OCR, ECAR, and PER from raw data; deal with outlying
    measurements in both background and experimental wells; calculate various
    experimental parameters; generate summary summary statistics; and aggregate 
    multiple experiments. 
